data.description: OPEN HOUSE - SATURDAY, JANUARY 27TH, 12PM-2PM.  Welcome home!  This beautiful, well designed home sits on a premium lot in Sunbury's finest Northstar Community.  This home has it all!  Brand new custom kitchen - great for entertaining, two story great room, large master retreat, bonus room - making a great kids playroom or man cave, loft, two oversized guest bedrooms and a backyard with amazing sunsets ready to make your own. This golf course community makes you feel like you are living at a resort day in and day out!  You don't want to miss this one!
